{"id":292885,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-维权人士刘沙沙贵州兴义监狱举牌关注著/","date":"2013-05-10T05:46:31Z","modified":"2015-12-22T22:44:51Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士刘沙沙贵州兴义监狱举牌关注著名政治犯陈西（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><em>（维权网信息员李军报道）在春节期间声援四川政治犯刘贤斌、陈卫，三八探访刘霞之后，著名维权人士刘沙沙继续她的“自由中国政治犯”之行。</em></div>\n<div><em> </em></div>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日上午，维权人士刘沙沙和香港保钓船长杨匡，来到远在贵州边远山区的贵州兴义市兴义监狱，为关押在此的良心犯陈西先生举牌：“陈西无罪”，并向监狱递交了致贵州省监狱管理局，贵州省司法厅、兴义监狱的《建议书》，建议书内容包括“允许非直系亲属探望陈西、存钱、送生活用品书籍等，允许陈西夫人有探望留宿权，以尽人伦人道”等。</p>\n<div></div>\n<div>前几日，刘沙沙和香港保钓船长杨匡一起在长沙黄兴路上，拉横幅“官员公布财产”，声援北京和江西因要求官员公布财产而被关押的公民们。</div>\n<div><em> </em></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Hrc68B8d_sY/UYyIet4zv2I/AAAAAAAAhtg/biCLXUeBLTg/s1600/1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Hrc68B8d_sY/UYyIet4zv2I/AAAAAAAAhtg/biCLXUeBLTg/s400/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eOBIVwJ6Jr0/UYyIgD7Q5oI/AAAAAAAAhto/23hLhCtvg3I/s1600/2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eOBIVwJ6Jr0/UYyIgD7Q5oI/AAAAAAAAhto/23hLhCtvg3I/s400/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"213\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4gcLDg3SwHU/UYyIhoski9I/AAAAAAAAhtw/R2r_3SvP_0M/s1600/3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4gcLDg3SwHU/UYyIhoski9I/AAAAAAAAhtw/R2r_3SvP_0M/s400/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"283\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mfdtgYgw2lA/UYyInyuzswI/AAAAAAAAht4/5UzLZCIrqkw/s1600/%E9%95%BF%E6%B2%99%EF%BC%8C%E9%BB%84%E5%85%B4%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%82.JPG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mfdtgYgw2lA/UYyInyuzswI/AAAAAAAAht4/5UzLZCIrqkw/s400/%E9%95%BF%E6%B2%99%EF%BC%8C%E9%BB%84%E5